# Celestina workspace — root ignore rules.
# Per-project .gitignore files still apply within each subtree; these are a
# catch-all so build output never lands in the monorepo regardless of depth.

# Rust build output
**/target/

# CMake / Qt build output
**/build/
**/cmake-build-*/
**/CMakeFiles/
CMakeCache.txt
cmake_install.cmake
Makefile
compile_commands.json

# Qt generated
*.qmlc
qmldir.qmltypes
.qmlls.ini

# Editor / OS cruft
.DS_Store
*.swp
*~
